downloadTitle: Telemetry in Office 2013: A new way to Assess Office Compatibility
downloadDescription: This poster explains and illustrates what Office Telemetry is, what's monitored in Office 2013, and how telemetry data is collected. It also lists and describes all the components of Office Telemetry.
